Territorial view from park.

40 open boat slip with 5 overhang in Anchor Cove. Fingers on both sides for easy loading and boarding. 30 amp power post and room for your own dock box. The current slows, a distance from the slip, so docking is easy. Clubhouse with showers and restrooms, picnic area for BBQs, fish cleaning and crab cooking stations, laundry w/ lending library. Located in the heart of Old Town, just a short walk to restaurants and shops. The Harbormaster lives on-site, and liveaboard is allowed for Members. Moor your boat, at the Gateway to the San Juan Islands. Great news - Seller will pay the upcoming assessment due in September!
